<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ezekiel%27s_vision.jpg" class="image" title="Ezekiel's &quot;chariot vision&quot;, by Matthaeus Merian (1593-1650)."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c6/Ezekiel%27s_vision.jpg/180px-Ezekiel%27s_vision.jpg" width="180" height="139" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Ezekiel%27s_vision.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
